    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Try </p>\n\n<pre><code>String[] splited = str.split(\"\\\\s\");\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/essential/regex/pre_char_classes.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://download.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/essential/regex/pre_char_classes.html</a></p>\n"
