    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p><strong>Simple to Spit String by Space</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>    String CurrentString = \"First Second Last\";\n    String[] separated = CurrentString.split(\" \");\n\n    for (int i = 0; i &lt; separated.length; i++) {\n\n         if (i == 0) {\n             Log.d(\"FName ** \", \"\" + separated[0].trim() + \"\\n \");\n         } else if (i == 1) {\n             Log.d(\"MName ** \", \"\" + separated[1].trim() + \"\\n \");\n         } else if (i == 2) {\n             Log.d(\"LName ** \", \"\" + separated[2].trim());\n         }\n     }\n</code></pre>\n"
