    "body" : "<p>Here is a method to trim a String that has a \",\" or white space</p>\n\n<pre><code>private String shorterName(String s){\n        String[] sArr = s.split(\"\\\\,|\\\\s+\");\n        String output = sArr[0];\n\n        return output;\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
